title: Warriors and Worthies-Arms and Armor Through the Ages (History)

Warriors and Worthies: Arms and Armor Through the Ages

Therefore, since earliest times Some of a man's most prized possessions have been his weapons, and the oldest specialized craft in the history of human civilization is hat of the smith, the maker of weapons for hunting and fighting.
